扮識英文，扮唔睇字幕(但又有人去搵盜版睇簡體字幕)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"無用tg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係你想問乜,係呢到問啦 (橫掂你都會post篇文)<br />\n我都係放工用空餘時間譯姐,我份工本身同翻譯一d關係都冇<br />\n而且我其實係理科仔,AL中英文叫做合格咁樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2c45effb0480d85a8e84ec07a72625f605383b","tid":1157411,"uid":230777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d058be0b5f823946198f232d1b51f39d8affdfa9","tid":1157411,"uid":41500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2e450c32eebf8cbdd12ca98c41e5026cddfc09c","tid":1157411,"uid":230777,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbe55e9eac3093fe3c2c35b3d37b2c7f8b1c61ec","tid":1157411,"uid":41500,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:15:14.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n根本個問題源頭係game廠唔出繁體<br />\n<br />\n各位如果有上開steam,會發現好多中/小型game廠同indie制作都剩係得殘體<br />\n<br />\n殘體玩家一來多,中/細game廠實主動整佢先,二來強國撚佢地真係好積極將外語翻譯做殘體 (睇下各個層面字幕組就知)<br />\n與其屌一個直播台主用殘體,不如聯絡game廠出繁體/自己做好過<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有幫過幾隻steam indie game整繁體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFt9HPX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFt9HPX.png&h=7ce59ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4uUqym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4uUqym.png&h=6fa16dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/910880/Mad_Tower_Tycoon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F910880%2FMad_Tower_Tycoon%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=a13e378d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/910880/Mad_Tower_Tycoon/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/341000/Mad_Games_Tycoon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F341000%2FMad_Games_Tycoon%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9a4f58a